Constructed in 2001, This Class B 34,560 SF office building offers multiply tenant's space. The property sits on 3.10 acres which has around 100 parking lot spaces, which make's it convenient for employees.

Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Direct entry space for most spaces with no common area
Individual tenant washrooms for most spaces
Convenient parking close to individual tenant entries
Tenant identity on building monument signs
Move-in ready and custom suites available

Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: Located in Lombard in the center of DuPage county, access is convenient to all directions via I-355 and I-88.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Mature trees, extensive landscaping, ponds, and open space create a different kind of office environment. This natural beauty can be enjoyed not only from your office window but also from outdoor gathering areas and walking paths. The 35 acre setting features seven one-story buildings contain over 260,000 square feet of various size space.
